## Urgency Mechanics

### 1. Slot Counter
- "847 de 1,000 plazas disponibles"
- Displayed in header (desktop) and sticky bar (mobile)
- Updates in real-time from database
- When slots < 100: Show in red/warning color

### 2. Countdown Timer
- "Faltan XX dÃ­as para la fecha lÃ­mite"
- Based on decree deadline (placeholder: December 31, 2026)
- Displayed on landing page hero and dashboard

### 3. Personal Reservation
- After eligibility: "Tu plaza #847 estÃ¡ reservada por 7 dÃ­as"
- Countdown timer on their dashboard
- Email reminder at 24h, 72h, and day 7

### 4. Social Proof
- "89 personas se inscribieron esta semana"
- Shown on payment confirmation screens
- Real number from database

