## API Routes

```
POST /api/eligibility          â†’ Process eligibility check
POST /api/auth/register        â†’ Create account
POST /api/auth/login           â†’ Login
POST /api/auth/logout          â†’ Logout
GET  /api/user                 â†’ Get current user
PUT  /api/user                 â†’ Update user profile

POST /api/documents/upload     â†’ Upload document
GET  /api/documents            â†’ List user's documents
DELETE /api/documents/:id      â†’ Delete document

POST /api/payments/create-checkout â†’ Create Stripe checkout session
POST /api/payments/webhook     â†’ Stripe webhook handler
GET  /api/payments             â†’ List user's payments

GET  /api/stats                â†’ Get global stats (slots, social proof)
GET  /api/progress             â†’ Get user's phase progress

POST /api/referral/generate    â†’ Generate referral code
GET  /api/referral/stats       â†’ Get referral stats
```

