## Notes for Claude Code

- This is a REAL app, not a demo â€” production-ready code required
- Supabase handles auth, database, and file storage â€” don't reinvent
- Stripe Checkout (embedded) is simpler than custom payment forms
- Mobile-first design is critical â€” most users on phones
- The urgency mechanics (slot counter, timers) are KEY to conversion
- Test the payment flow thoroughly â€” this is where money happens
- Keep the UI clean and simple â€” users may have limited tech experience
- Spanish only for MVP (no i18n needed yet)
